        "title": "Remove ClawScan note feature",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Remove ClawScan publisher notes from skill/plugin publish flows, settings UI, dashboard/security audit surfaces, CLI flags, package schemas, OpenAPI output, and user/operator docs.\n- Remove ClawScan note text from the LLM security prompt and publish/rescan inputs so legacy note fields are ignored instead of treated as scanner context.\n- Keep optional legacy database fields/source enum compatibility for old rows/jobs while omitting note fields from active public/query response shapes.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `bun run ci:packages`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run test convex/packages.public.test.ts convex/skills.staffAuditLogs.test.ts src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx src/routes/-dashboard.test.tsx`\n- `bunx vitest run src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/plugins-publish-route.test.tsx src/__tests__/skills-publish-route.test.tsx src/components/SkillSecurityScanResults.test.tsx convex/lib/securityPrompt.test.ts convex/llmEval.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts convex/skills.backportLatest.test.ts packages/clawhub/src/cli/commands/publish.test.ts packages/clawhub/src/cli/commands/packages.test.ts packages/schema/src/schemas.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n\n## UI Proof\n\n- Browser smoke checked `/skills/publish`, `/plugins/publish`, and `/plugins/example/settings` locally.\n- Screenshot: `/tmp/clawhub-clawscan-note-removal-plugin-publish.png`\n\n## Notes\n\n- `bunx convex codegen` could not refresh generated files because the local Convex config endpoint at `127.0.0.1:3216` returned `500 InternalServerError`; `convex/_generated/api.d.ts` was updated manually and the TypeScript/build gates passed.\n",
